			<div class="content" id="post-content-3631454">
									

<p>This started out as the song written by Frederick von Hayek that Adebowale talks about towards the end. I didn't think that concept had any true soul, so I made this instead.</p>
<p>Also: while this an AWCY GoI-Format, I don't see Adebowale as a true member of AWCY. Rather, they are an independent anartist who displays pieces at the dicennial conventions run by AWCY, which tend to be a bit more mainstream than pure AWCY.</p>
<p>EDIT: I forgot that the AWCY conventions are dicennial, not annual. This got bumped back to 1994 from 1998 to make it fit.</p>
<hr />
<p>If you liked this thing and would like to read some comments about it, or check out other things I've written, head to <a href="/stormbreath">my author page</a> for more!</p>

