															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009732); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009732&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164616" alt="Moklin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009732)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moklin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009732); return false;" >Moklin</a></span> <span class="odate time_1512171457 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Dec 2017 23:37</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3643998">
									

<p>A fantastic addition to AWCY. I especially liked how mundane the most beautiful thing Adebowale has seen is, and how they have none of the stuff they're asking for - it makes them feel very human.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Typos?</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">IDK&nbsp;adebowale's&nbsp;english&nbsp;might&nbsp;just&nbsp;be&nbsp;bad</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>For the creation of the piece:</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This bit doesn't to show up in any other AWCY format, though I'll forgive it as nobody can seem to agree on what exactly the format <em>is</em>.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Twenty years, I saw the most beautiful thing</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Twenty years <em>ago</em>, I saw the most beautiful thing</p>
<blockquote>
<p>had ever seen or would ever seen.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>had ever seen or would ever <em>see</em>.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I will not speak of what happened it.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I will not speak of what happened <em>to</em> it.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I could have survived in my old home, a horrid and brutal life.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Kinda seems like poetic prose, but I don't know.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>it still trapped in Pandora's Amphora.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Not entirely sure how I'd fix this one, though I do understand what it's trying to say.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>It was basic kindness</p>
</blockquote>
<p>It was <em>a</em> basic kindness? Not sure if this is just prose or not.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

